      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HERE'S RYDER (6) has a strong winning strike-rate over this journey with four wins and a placing from six tries. Placed last time (17.37) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 5.5 lengths. Looks suited and should go close. SWING BY (7) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 17.32 beating Hudson's Dream. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Should be in this for a long way. SHUFFLE (8) placed in a Grade 5 when a 2.75 lengths third this course and distance last time in a personal Best Time (17.18) and also clocked one of the quickest times on the card. Strong latest and expected to measure up. NUGGET ROBERTS (1) is worth including after a top-three finish most recently.",
